    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_5_427-439",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "427-439",
      "markText": "人生天地间，忽如远行客。",
      "totalCount": 1216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=427&rangeEnd=439",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=427&rangeEnd=439"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_17_387-481",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "387-481",
      "markText": "生年不满百，常怀千岁忧。 昼短苦夜长，何不秉烛游！ 为乐当及时，何能待来兹？",
      "totalCount": 864,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=387&rangeEnd=481",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=387&rangeEnd=481"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_12_386-562",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "386-562",
      "markText": "迢迢牵牛星，皎皎河汉女。 纤纤擢素手，札札弄机杼。 终日不成章，泣涕零如雨。 河汉清且浅，相去复几许。 盈盈一水间，脉脉不得语。",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=562",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=562"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_6_550-643",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "550-643",
      "markText": "人生寄一世，奄忽若飙尘。 何不策高足，先据要路津。 无为守贫贱，坎轲长苦辛",
      "totalCount": 675,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=550&rangeEnd=643",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=550&rangeEnd=643"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_7_632-644",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "632-644",
      "markText": "不惜歌者苦，但伤知音稀。",
      "totalCount": 480,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=644",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=644"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_9_550-603",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "550-603",
      "markText": "昔我同门友，高举振六翮。 不念携手好，弃我如遗迹。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=550&rangeEnd=603",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=550&rangeEnd=603"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_5_673-685",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "673-685",
      "markText": "极宴娱心意，戚戚何所迫？",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=673&rangeEnd=685",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=673&rangeEnd=685"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_8_386-521",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "386-521",
      "markText": "涉江采芙蓉，兰泽多芳草。 采之欲遗谁，所思在远道。 还顾望旧乡，长路漫浩浩。 同心而离居，忧伤以终老。",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=521",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=521"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_15_592-604",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "592-604",
      "markText": "人生忽如寄，寿无金石固。",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=592&rangeEnd=604",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=592&rangeEnd=604"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_11_386-521",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "386-521",
      "markText": "庭中有奇树，绿叶发华滋。 攀条折其荣，将以遗所思。 馨香盈怀袖，路远莫致之。 此物何足贵，但感别经时。",
      "totalCount": 377,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=521",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=521"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_7_386-398",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "386-398",
      "markText": "西北有高楼，上与浮云齐。",
      "totalCount": 375,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=398",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=398"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_3_632-644",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "632-644",
      "markText": "思君令人老，岁月忽已晚。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=644",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=644"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_3_386-480",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "386-480",
      "markText": "行行重行行，与君生别离。 相去万余里，各在天一涯。 道路阻且长，会面安可知。",
      "totalCount": 350,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=480",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=480"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_20_387-563",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "387-563",
      "markText": "客从远方来，遗我一端绮。 相去万余里，故人心尚尔。 文彩双鸳鸯，裁为合欢被。 著以长相思，缘以结不解。 以胶投漆中，谁能别离此？",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=387&rangeEnd=563",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=387&rangeEnd=563"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_13_592-604",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "592-604",
      "markText": "奄忽随物化，荣名以为宝。",
      "totalCount": 304,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=592&rangeEnd=604",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=592&rangeEnd=604"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_3_509-521",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "509-521",
      "markText": "胡马依北风，越鸟巢南枝。",
      "totalCount": 273,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=509&rangeEnd=521",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=509&rangeEnd=521"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_19_510-645",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "510-645",
      "markText": "客从远方来，遗我一书札。 上言长相思，下言久离别。 置书怀袖中，三岁字不灭。 一心抱区区，惧君不识察。",
      "totalCount": 273,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=510&rangeEnd=645",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=510&rangeEnd=645"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046425_14_592-604",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "592-604",
      "markText": "燕赵多佳人，美者颜如玉。",
      "totalCount": 225,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046425&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=592&rangeEnd=604",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/921326b0813ab78a2g015cfe?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=592&rangeEnd=604"
    },
